meta {
  name: 00 Setup
  seq: 1
}

docs {
  Pre-flight requests. Run these first; they save tokens to env vars used by
  every subsequent request:

  - orgAdminToken          → ORG_ADMIN of MULTI_STORE_ORG (non-partner).
  - storeAdminToken        → STORE_ADMIN of a child store.
  - partnerOrgAdminToken   → ORG_ADMIN of a partner organization.
}
